ultrasonic equipment which is used to diagnose problems with
internal organs and check the health of fetuses, the official news
agency said. Its products will go both for export and for domestic
use.
   ``Unfortunately, there is a shortage of such equipment in the
U.S.S.R.'' Serdyuk told Tass. ``This is especially true of
high-class systems, like those produced by Elscint.''
